{"id":570499,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/10/【弄个大新闻】困难群众成网络热词-相关商品/","date":"2017-10-20T03:02:01Z","modified":"2018-07-16T01:41:52Z","title":"【弄个大新闻】“困难群众”成网络热词 相关商品遭禁售","content":"<p>十九大期间，习近平曾说过的“我最牵挂的还是困难群众”又再一次被党媒拿来反复宣传。这一次，“困难群众”突然成为网民用来自我调侃的热词。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_570504\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/我最牵挂的还是困难群众.jpeg\"><img class=\"wp-image-570504\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/我最牵挂的还是困难群众.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"359\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/我最牵挂的还是困难群众.jpeg 955w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/我最牵挂的还是困难群众-300x239.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/我最牵挂的还是困难群众-768x613.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">央视节目截图</span></p></div>\n<p>淘宝上很快就出现了印有“困难群众”字样的商品：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_570507\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/淘宝困难群众商品.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-570507\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/淘宝困难群众商品.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"711\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/淘宝困难群众商品.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/淘宝困难群众商品-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">网络图片</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_570503\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/困难群众商品.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-570503\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/困难群众商品.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"430\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/困难群众商品.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/困难群众商品-279x300.jpg 279w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">网络图片</span></p></div>\n<p><strong>然而才过一天，就有电商被勒令下架出现“困难群众”字眼的商品。截至发稿时，发布下架通知截图的微博已被和谐。</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_570508\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/说说而已的，你们就别当真了-吃瓜-来自连扯-微博.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-570508\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/说说而已的，你们就别当真了-吃瓜-来自连扯-微博.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"599\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/说说而已的，你们就别当真了-吃瓜-来自连扯-微博.png 1209w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/说说而已的，你们就别当真了-吃瓜-来自连扯-微博-275x300.png 275w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/说说而已的，你们就别当真了-吃瓜-来自连扯-微博-768x837.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/说说而已的，你们就别当真了-吃瓜-来自连扯-微博-940x1024.png 940w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">被删微博截图</span></p></div>\n<blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>与“困难群众”相关的商品不得售卖</li>\n<li>自行排查已上线的相关商品、宣传用语，若发现困难群众字眼及相关含义的商品、宣传用语请立即清除</li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n<p>为验证该通知的真实性，中国数字时代编辑在淘宝检索了关键词“困难群众”，<strong>搜索结果中没有任何与这次网络热词有关的产品。同时，却已有“机智”的商户用“大大牵挂群众”来代替“困难群众”，这更进一步证实了该词已成为敏感词的事实。</strong>也有不少微博用户表示自己发布或转发“困难群众”相关内容的微博被删除。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_570505\" style=\"width: 539px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/淘宝困难群众.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-570505\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/淘宝困难群众.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"529\" height=\"439\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/淘宝困难群众.jpg 1600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/淘宝困难群众-300x249.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/淘宝困难群众-768x637.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/淘宝困难群众-1024x850.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 529px) 100vw, 529px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">淘宝“困难群众”搜索结果截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_570506\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/淘宝困难群众卫衣2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-570506\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/淘宝困难群众卫衣2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"254\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/淘宝困难群众卫衣2.jpg 1896w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/淘宝困难群众卫衣2-300x139.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/淘宝困难群众卫衣2-768x355.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/淘宝困难群众卫衣2-1024x473.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">有“机智”的商户用“大大牵挂群众”来代替已成为敏感词的“困难群众”；网页截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_570502\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/困难群众.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-570502\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/困难群众.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"342\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/困难群众.jpg 1330w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/困难群众-300x195.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/困难群众-768x500.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/困难群众-1024x667.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/困难群众-230x150.jpg 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">有微博用户抱怨自己转发“困难群众”的内容被删；微博截图</span></p></div>\n<p>另外，习近平称要让中国到2020年全面建成小康社会，而根据官方标准，家庭年收入高于36万的才称得上小康家庭，这也为“困难群众”一词增加了热度。网民们纷纷吐槽自己又“给祖国拖后腿”，还出现了类似“2020年全面脱贫，届时是要杀我灭口吗”这样的网络段子。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_570509\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/6b13f227ly1fkmiyhjf06j20qx0qoag2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-570509\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/6b13f227ly1fkmiyhjf06j20qx0qoag2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"397\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/6b13f227ly1fkmiyhjf06j20qx0qoag2.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/6b13f227ly1fkmiyhjf06j20qx0qoag2-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/6b13f227ly1fkmiyhjf06j20qx0qoag2-300x297.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/6b13f227ly1fkmiyhjf06j20qx0qoag2-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">网络图片</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_570501\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/全面脱贫.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-570501\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/全面脱贫.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"305\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/全面脱贫.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/全面脱贫-300x229.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">网络图片</span></p></div>\n<p>另外需要指出的是，“困难群众”比“屁民”、“驴民”等草泥马语要温和许多，使用者中不乏向党国“撒娇”的小粉红。但，老大哥显然并不这么看。</p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[30303,10782,31745,8616,32616]}